<item>
            <title>[HBASE-7539] when region is closed, the closing server should null out location in meta in process</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-7539</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;No point in having stale META record when the server that put it has already closed the region.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12627090">HBASE-7539</key>
            <summary>when region is closed, the closing server should null out location in meta in process</summary>
